(146, 1, '2015-11-23 13:27:30', '2015-11-23 12:27:30', '<code>Azaya Villa in Chiang Mai</code>\r\n\r\nNestled among the hills of Mae Rim in northern Thailand, Azaya Villas offers creatively designed villas with private pools.\r\n\r\nThe spacious villas include a living area with a flat-screen TV and home entertainment system. Villas also have kitchen facilities, a private sun deck, and tropical gardens.\r\n\r\nGuests can rent a bicycle to explore the area, then unwind with an in-villa massage or beauty treatment. Staff can assist with tour bookings, car rental, and laundry services.\r\n\r\nPrivate chefs can prepare meals for guests, including barbecue or special Thai dinners. The villas offer grocery shopping services for guests’ convenience.\r\n\r\nAzaya Villas is the 2.5 km from the popular Jirung Health Spa Village. It is a 25-minute drive from Chiang Mai International Airport and Chiang Mai''s city centre.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://orientreizen.eu.pn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/villa6_rate.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-142" src="http://orientreizen.eu.pn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/villa6_rate-300x169.jpg" alt="villa6_rate" width="300" height="169" /></a><a href="http://orientreizen.eu.pn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/thailand-kaart.jpg"><img class="alignnone  wp-image-144" src="http://orientreizen.eu.pn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/thailand-kaart-176x300.jpg" alt="thailand-kaart" width="174" height="297" /></a>\r\n\r\nFaciliteiten\r\n\r\nBuiten\r\n<div id="hp_facilities_box" class="facilitiesChecklist">\r\n<div class="facilitiesChecklistSection">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Barbecuevoorzieningen</li>\r\n	<li>Buitenzwembad</li>\r\n	<li>Tuin</li>\r\n	<li>Zonneterras</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="facilitiesChecklistSection">\r\n<h5></h5>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="facilitiesChecklistSection">\r\n<h5>Activiteiten</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Golfbaan (binnen 3 km)</li>\r\n	<li>Fietsen</li>\r\n	<li>Wellnesscentrum</li>\r\n	<li>Massage</li>\r\n	<li>Bubbelbad</li>\r\n	<li>